description:
[P][US1] Add leaf constructors to src/MCP/Trace/Server.hs:
- ServerInit { serverName, serverVersion }
- ServerShutdown
- ServerInitialized { clientInfo }
- ServerCapabilityNegotiation { negotiatedCapabilities }
- ServerStateChange { fromState, toState }

Ref: specs/003-structured-tracing/data-model.md ServerTrace

[P][US1] Add leaf constructors to src/MCP/Trace/Protocol.hs:
- ProtocolRequestReceived { requestId, method }
- ProtocolResponseSent { requestId, isError }
- ProtocolNotificationReceived { method }
- ProtocolParseError { errorMessage, rawInput }
- ProtocolMethodNotFound { requestId, method }
- ProtocolInvalidParams { requestId, method, errorDetail }

Ref: specs/003-structured-tracing/data-model.md ProtocolTrace

[P][US2] Add leaf constructors to src/MCP/Trace/OAuth.hs:
- OAuthClientRegistration { clientId, clientName }
- OAuthAuthorizationRequest { clientId, scopes, hasState }
- OAuthLoginPageServed { sessionId }
- OAuthLoginAttempt { username, success }
- OAuthAuthorizationGranted/Denied
- OAuthTokenExchange { grantType, success }
- OAuthTokenRefresh { success }
- OAuthSessionExpired { sessionId }
- OAuthValidationError { errorType, errorDetail }

Ref: specs/003-structured-tracing/data-model.md OAuthTrace

[P][US2] Add leaf constructors to src/MCP/Trace/HTTP.hs:
- HTTPServerStarting { port, baseUrl }
- HTTPServerStarted
- HTTPRequestReceived { path, method, hasAuth }
- HTTPAuthRequired { path }
- HTTPAuthSuccess { userId }
- HTTPAuthFailure { reason }

Note: HTTPProtocol and HTTPOAuth composites already exist from skeleton

Ref: specs/003-structured-tracing/data-model.md HTTPTrace

[P][US3] Add leaf constructors to src/MCP/Trace/StdIO.hs:
- StdIOMessageReceived { messageSize }
- StdIOMessageSent { messageSize }
- StdIOReadError { errorMessage }
- StdIOEOF

Note: StdIOProtocol composite already exists from skeleton

Ref: specs/003-structured-tracing/data-model.md StdIOTrace
